Product Description▼▲
Find biblical ways to resolve conflict and communicate effectively. Dr. Stuart Scott, Professor of Biblical Counseling, describes the principles and skills of good communication, where conflicts come from, sinful ways to resolve conflict, and God-honoring ways to reconcile.

